        "source_sentence": "此即第一略敘彼土佛事也。",
        "translation": "This is the first one, which briefly describes the Buddha's activities in that land.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388b29_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時彼佛即告第一大弟子(至)并可禮敬請決所疑。",
        "translation": "It was then that the Buddha addressed the first great disciple (to) and asked him to pay homage and respect and resolve his doubts.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c02_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c03_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慧朗曰。",
        "translation": "Huilang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c03_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此第二彼佛命使來。",
        "translation": "\"This is the second time that Buddha ordered his messengers to come.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c03_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時無邊身菩薩摩訶薩(至)所有威德悉滅無餘。",
        "translation": "At that point, the limitless-body bodhisattva Mahāsattva(-to) had all of his authoritative qualities extinguished without remainder.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c04_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c05_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慧朗曰。",
        "translation": "Huilang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c05_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此第三敘時眾驚怪也。",
        "translation": "\"This is the third account of when the multitude was astonished.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c05_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時文殊師利法王子(至)如來不久當般涅槃。",
        "translation": "It was then that Mañjuśrī, Prince of the Dharma (to) the Tathāgata would soon [enter] parinirvāṇa.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c06_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c07_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慧朗曰。",
        "translation": "Huilang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c07_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此第四敘文殊安慰大眾也。",
        "translation": "\"This is the fourth account in which Mañjuśrī comforts the multitude.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c07_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時大眾一切悉見(至)如是流布大乘經典。",
        "translation": "At the time, the whole crowd saw (to) thus disseminate the great vehicle sūtras.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c08_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c09_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慧朗曰。",
        "translation": "Huilang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c09_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此第五敘菩薩神力。",
        "translation": "\"This fifth describes the bodhisattva's spiritual power.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c09_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時無邊身菩薩(至)如來不久當般涅槃。",
        "translation": "It was then that the limitless-body bodhisattva (arrived) that the Tathāgata would soon [enter] parinirvāṇa.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c10_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c10_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慧朗曰。",
        "translation": "Huilang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c11_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此第六明菩薩以神力。",
        "translation": "\"The sixth here explains that the bodhisattva uses supernormal powers.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c11_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "令身中眾生。",
        "translation": "It causes sentient beings in his body.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c11_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得法悟也。",
        "translation": "They'll attain enlightenment of the Dharma.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c12_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時無邊身菩薩(至)餘無能見是菩薩身其量邊際。",
        "translation": "At that point, the limitless-body bodhisattva (to) nothing else could see the limit of the bodhisattva's body's capacity.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c13_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c14_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慧朗曰。",
        "translation": "Huilang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c14_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第七明以神力辦供。",
        "translation": "\"The seventh clarification is to make offerings with supernormal powers.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c14_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時無邊身菩薩及其眷屬(至)如是三請悉亦不受。",
        "translation": "At the time, the limitless-body bodhisattva and his retinue (to) accept all three of these requests.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c15_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c16_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慧朗曰。",
        "translation": "Huilang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c16_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第八明以供上佛。",
        "translation": "\"The eighth clarification was to make an offering to the Buddha.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c16_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛不受。",
        "translation": "The Buddha didn't accept it.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c16_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時無邊身菩薩及其眷屬(至)却住一面皆亦如是。",
        "translation": "At the time, the limitless-body bodhisattva and his retinue (up to) the point where they stayed to one side were likewise.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c17_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c18_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慧朗曰。",
        "translation": "Huilang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c18_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舉十方同到者總結。",
        "translation": "\"Let's summarize this by saying that they all arrived together in the ten directions.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c18_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時娑羅雙樹吉祥福地(至)見諸佛土亦復如是。",
        "translation": "It was then that the Śāla Twin Trees auspicious and Blessed Land (to) see all the buddha-lands was likewise.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c19_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c20_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慧朗曰。",
        "translation": "Huilang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c20_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此辨佛神力有兩章。",
        "translation": "\"This discernment of the Buddha's spiritual powers has two chapters.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c20_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此即第一光明變穢為淨也。",
        "translation": "This is the first one, which is the transformation of defilement into purity.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c20_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時如來面門所出(至)身諸毛孔流血灑地。",
        "translation": "It was then that the blood flowing from the pores of the Tathāgata's body emanated from the face of the Tathāgata (to) the ground.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c22_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c23_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "法瑤曰。",
        "translation": "Fayao said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c23_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "化緣周畢。",
        "translation": "\"The circle of transformation is complete.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c23_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "表涅槃之相也。",
        "translation": "It shows the aspect of nirvāṇa.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c23_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有三種。",
        "translation": "There are three kinds.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c23_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一眾生心淨。",
        "translation": "One, the minds of sentient beings are purified.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c24_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二國土淨。",
        "translation": "Two, the land is purified.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c24_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三收光入口。",
        "translation": "Three, the harvesting of light and its entrance.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c24_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "收光入口。",
        "translation": "He receives the light and enters through.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c24_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則止教之相。",
        "translation": "This is the mark of the teaching of cessation.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c25_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "眾生心淨。",
        "translation": "The minds of sentient beings are purified.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c25_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則表化周。",
        "translation": "Then manifestation is complete.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c25_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "國土淨者。",
        "translation": "The land is purified.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c25_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則明行畢也。",
        "translation": "It then shows that his practice is complete.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c26_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慧朗曰。",
        "translation": "Huilang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c26_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此第二階。",
        "translation": "\"This is the second stage.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c26_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示涅槃之相也。",
        "translation": "It shows the character of nirvāṇa.",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c26_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大般涅槃經集解卷第三",
        "translation": "Mahāparinirvāṇa-sūtra, Collected and Explained, Volume 3",
        "source": "T37n1763_003:0388c28_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    }
]